  "bodyHtml": "There are 2 ways to find the amount of the deferred payment.<br>You can find it in the “Invoices - Pending Invoices” tab in the Back Office.<br> \n<div><img alt=\"Screenshot 2022-04-26 at 11.25.08.png\" src=\"/ssc/servlet/rtaImage?eid=ka0Sb0000006gRB&amp;feoid=00N3X00000M5fJO&amp;refid=0EM3X000008UAOi\"></img><br>Alternatively, you can access this information in your last invoice under: <i>“Sommes retenues à titre préventif”</i></div>"
}